{"tid":2217450,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"外電指最少兩間銀行停止向恒大授出信貸額度","createTime":"2020-09-25T12:30:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-25T12:46:32.000Z","uid":5195,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"bb33afb2897e0166a90f7c1f8cba55e3642ed318","tid":2217450,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T12:30:45.000Z","msg":"中國恒大(<a href=\"http://03333.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F03333.HK&d=awVbgeYyyy76%2F43Y8QfwzvQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=0f891ec6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">03333.HK</a>)早前指網上流傳有關重組情況的文件是偽造，但外電引述知情人士說，有份借貸予恒大的金融機構，至少有5間中國的銀行及2間信託機構，在昨晚召開緊急會議，審視涉及恒大的貸款及抵押品。 其中，民生銀行涉及恒大的款項有約290億元人民幣，是銀行之中最多，而最少2間銀行已經決定停止向恒大授出未用信貸額度，據統計，在5030億信貸額度之中，有3020億元仍未使用。 中國恒大股價跌逾8%，報13.88元，跌1.34元，恒大汽車(<a href=\"http://00708.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00708.HK&d=awVbgeYyyy76%2F43Y8QfwzvQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=aea25510\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00708.HK</a>)跌16%，報16.14元，跌3.14元。 <br />\n<br />\n恒大早前曾經引入多名的大型策略投資者，萬一未能在明年1月31日之前，獲批在深交所借殼上市，他們可以要求取回投資在恒大的款項，假如投資者拒絕再延長期限，恒大將被追回1300億元人民幣，相當於現時持有現金的92%。 <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/finance/2358917\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Ffinance%2F2358917&d=awVbgeYyyy76%2F43Y8QfwzvQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=e4b168ba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/finance/2358917</a>"},{"pid":"ec231c4d04952b7b81650491b9567c28f8a695ac","tid":2217450,"uid":346701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T12:37:24.000Z","msg":"隻含池汽車cap唔夠水？"},{"pid":"60531191db1e77806b8f24875de6a32ec986d625","tid":2217450,"uid":300006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T12:40:19.000Z","msg":"不造謠，不信謠<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47677326ce2d901b920886418ab9daf05367de4a","tid":2217450,"uid":30040,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"202